# ============================================
# FIELD SPECIFICATIONS:
# ============================================
# Providers:
#   - specialties: Comma-separated values (e.g., "Turf restoration,Soil remediation")
#   - insurance: Yes/No or True/False
#   - experience: Number of years (e.g., 12)
#   - successRate: Percentage as decimal (e.g., 96.5)
#
# Problems:
#   - latitude/longitude: Decimal coordinates (e.g., 11.0420, 77.0269)
#   - severity: Low, Medium, High, or Critical
#   - status: Open, In Progress, Resolved, or Pending
#   - priority: Low, Medium, High, or Critical
#   - images: Pipe-separated URLs (e.g., "url1|url2|url3")
#   - tags: Comma-separated values (e.g., "water,urgent,health-hazard")
